-    ``'interrupt'`` (user typed mid-stream) and ``'user_interrupted'``
-    (ESC) differently — for ``'interrupt'`` it only synthesizes
-    REJECT_MESSAGE on tools whose ``interruptBehavior() === 'cancel'``.
